snippet.title: They Came From Dimension X - Trailer 2: "Death May Serve Me Better"
snippet.description:
THEY CAME FROM DIMENSION X is sci-fi cosmic horror first person shooter where up can be down can be left can be right; where gravity is only as consistent as the ground your boots are stepping upon. Navigate labyrinthine research stations, strange alien planets and escheresque eldritch tombs that fold in upon and fold out of themselves while surviving your maddened colleagues, monstrous entities, and worse.

Play the demo!
